     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts mappingConsentementCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"mappingConsentementCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"hcmappingConsentementCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Groupe 1 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-consentement</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-authorization</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMConsentement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>authorization</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMConsentement.identifiantConsentement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>authorization.consent.id</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMConsentement.typeConsentement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>authorization.consent.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMConsentement.statutConsentement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>authorization.consent.statusCode=\"completed\"</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Groupe 2 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-authorization</code> to <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/fhir-clinical-document/STU1.1/StructureDefinition-consent-extension.html\">Consent Extensionversion : 1.1.0)</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td><td><b>Commentaire</b></td></tr><tr><td>authorization</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ConsentExtension.ValueReference.Consent</td><td>ValueReference.resolve().ofType(Consent)</td></tr><tr><td>authorization.consent.id</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ConsentExtension.ValueReference.Consent.identifier</td><td/></tr><tr><td>authorization.consent.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ConsentExtension.ValueReference.Consent.category</td><td/></tr><tr><td>authorization.consent.statusCode=\"completed\"</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:ConsentExtension.ValueReference.Consent.status:active</td><td/></tr></table></div><div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap mappingConsentementCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"en-mappingConsentementCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"en-hcmappingConsentementCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Group 1 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-consentement</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-authorization</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMConsentement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>authorization</td>